<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>271</hymn_number>
<title>JUSTAS I AM</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Timai hih ka hi panpih bei,
 Mahleh Na thisan kei din luong;
 Na kawma hung di'n nei sama,
 Aw Pathien Belam No, ka hung.

[V2]
 2. Timai hih ka hi, nei pawmin,
 Nen cheng theinna di'n ka hung hi;
 Na thisan ah gitloh thieng ding,
 Aw Pathien Belam No, ka hung.

[V3]
 3. Timai hih ka hi, nei pawmin,
 Nei ngaihdam a nei silthien di'n;
 Na thutiem chuh ka gin ziekin,
 Aw Pathien Belam No, ka hung.

[V4]
 4. Timai hih ka hi, Na hehpih -
 Na'n gitlohna cheng a hihmang;
 Tun Nangmah a mai hi dingin,
 Aw Pathien Belam No, ka hung.</lyrics>
</song>